हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Sold into a powerful noble family, a voiceless bride endures cruelty and manipulation from her tyrant husband. But as secrets unravel and false faces are exposed, her silence becomes her sharpest weapon. A sweeping tale of betrayal, power, and a woman’s unbreakable fight for dignity and freedom.
